<plot>A young man, John, reflects on his collection of photographs, recalling the memories every picture holds. This leads to the uncovering of John's most painful memory and regret. He now begins a journey for forgiveness. Caught between reflection and reality, John attempts to regain the love he lost, hoping to re-blossom his happiness before it wilts away forever.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?653338</url></doc>
